licity close\nbinaries may have lower mass ratios and the abundance of brown dwarfs to stars\nmay increase slightly. However, these latter two effects are quite weak and\nneed to be confirmed with larger samples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Jan 2019 19:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-15"}
