n of a collimated outflow with an opening angle of\nroughly 30 degrees. An expected mass outflow rate of 2E-7 or 4E-5 solar mass\nper yr is estimated by a relativistic jet-driven outflow or collimated stellar\nwinds, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Jan 2019 19:00:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-13"}
